{"tid":1506560,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"DLLM大公報","createTime":"2019-08-26T00:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:36:07.000Z","uid":293242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d6479395d757fd095b4fc9b507c24e3d36e7bd","tid":1506560,"uid":293242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:09:42.000Z","msg":"我樓下成日都有個廢老係到派大公報，我每次行過都會一邊怒啤住佢，一邊拎一份，等少一個廢老拎到。<br />\n<br />\n今日返工既時候，有班廢老照去拎大公報，找完係到罵d後生暴力，搞事，支持警察。<br />\n<br />\n我話d新聞係假既，班廢老開始罵我，仲愈來愈激動。<br />\n<br />\n想問問大家有咩方法可以令到呢d垃圾報紙消失？"},{"pid":"6391ce5ac9621177a19a3e5c91c6007f344504d2","tid":1506560,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:10:25.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxi8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=2566b058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2